UfoSighting.create! date: "2001-07-15", location: "Cateret, New Jersey", description: "At least 15 people, including 2 police officers, stopped their cars along the New Jersey Turnpike to view light formations in the night sky."
UfoSighting.create! date: "2004-03-05", location: "Mexico", description: "A drug-smuggling air-patrol recorded on infrared camera what some claimed to be UFOs. The footage was released by Jaime Maussan. The objects were however convincingly correlated with the burn-off flares of oil platforms."
UfoSighting.create! date: "2006-11-07", location:"Chicago, Illinois", description: "United Airlines employees and pilots claimed sightings of a saucer-shaped, unlit craft hovering over a Chicago O'Hare Airport terminal, before shooting up vertically"